name: KeyStorke
description:
A collaborative effort by AshTheMan and X_Whiteflame_X on their first-ever game jam. What do you think two 14 year-olds came up with?

Introducing KeyStroke!

This Game will make you RAGE! A 2D platformer where the key bindings...are not in your control! With the bindings changing every 15 seconds can you reach the end? Play to Find Out!
